Title: 'Winter looks better from Spring '
DateModified: '2019-03-10'
DatePublished: '2019-03-10'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/winter-looks-better-from-spring
SetInCountry: Austria
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Ana Barrios
AuthorCountry: Mexico
Text: Ema has just find out that her 4-year-old Jewish boyfriend is engaged to another
  Jewish girl, 'to get out from her  depression  she finds herself, Ema enters into
  a frightful depression, fear paralyzes her and feels that life has no meaning. Ema
  decides to take a trip to Europe. In Vienna, Ema meets Matthew on the train, a musician,
  who has just lost his girlfriend in a car accident. At first Ema and Mateo do not
  like each other, but as they begin to talk, they begin to develop a nice friendship
  that develops into a beautiful romance. Ema and Mateo travel together in Europe,
  they are  surprised by old stories, beautiful landscapes and talking about what
  they like most, music. This way both discover that there is life after the duel
  and that poetry is the encounter with the unexpected and that all you want is on
  the other side of fear-
